{"tid":1788392,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[真欖炒]其實澳門嘅春袋喺香港度, 香港做呢樣野澳門GDP即跌一半","createTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T04:17:09.000Z","uid":164730,"like":80,"dislike":361,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"89462bd3744e9730b9777fec43416a15ad7c7ba6","tid":1788392,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳門GDP咁高，<br />\n係澳門人水準高？唔係<br />\n係澳門政府勁？唔係<br />\n澳門醫療，基建，大學，政府服務（派錢除外），人材，法制水準都係好低<br />\n<br />\n純粹係因為佢係做啱一樣野：<strong>開放賭業，成為全中國唯一有合法賭場嘅地區，令到全中國啲賭金湧晒入去</strong><br />\n<br />\n假如中國有個垃圾三線城，開放毒品市場，果個垃圾城市都會因為係全球唯一一個合法交易毒品嘅城市，推到GDP全世界第一<br />\n個垃圾三線城GDP高唔代表高質素<br />\n<br />\n為咗唔好益澳門<br />\n我地可以一招欖炒澳門：立即開放賭業，邀請美國賭博公司落戶香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我包保開業後，澳門GDP即跌一半<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"699ab8b66599acf3b89f6de47d83fb343e118cca","tid":1788392,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf624c71a3fa459372784f63174cc42067b94315","tid":1788392,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698ca0472625a67da330d0a1fd16d401e29dcb52","tid":1788392,"uid":313964,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4bfa18bb8f5b3d158640b47ee6ea0fa05c7ece4","tid":1788392,"uid":36461,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"各區社區中心大變身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045439d7b229f2aaa65387eebbb906dfbe5750e6","tid":1788392,"uid":189109,"like":165,"dislike":3,"score":162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"20