7201a2076350762948862a0fca3427f8d4","tid":1788392,"uid":227177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"邊個比賭牌你？<br />\n唔係光明正大邊個㴝？<br />\n唔係想屌鳩你，但可否實際少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a61e7e3b02f835c99115a3d7fd368b5044e85e0","tid":1788392,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"海南島計畫開賭（上面吹風吹咗好耐）<br />\n依家土共諗法，香港嘅去馬交，馬交去海南<br />\n有冇人諗過"},{"pid":"cc034bcbec820cba72c1703f563095dd5af301e8","tid":1788392,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a61e7e3b02f835c99115a3d7fd368b5044e85e0","tid":1788392,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"海南島計畫開賭（上面吹風吹咗好耐）<br />\n依家土共諗法，香港嘅去馬交，馬交去海南<br />\n有冇人諗過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:56:26.000Z","msg":"當然，成功與否就喺另外一件事"},{"pid":"6170b600924503254c25e67ae92f2bc7a6c1c9e7","tid":1788392,"uid":300782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:56:47.000Z","msg":"澳門咁有錢<br />\n賭錢都要用港幣<br />\n<br />\n點解唔用支那幣"},{"pid":"41287a199e32f65069ce1b243ed8e236562049c8","tid":1788392,"uid":143826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89462bd3744e9730b9777fec43416a15ad7c7ba6","tid":1788392,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳門GDP咁高，<br />\n係澳門人水準高？唔係<br />\n係澳門政府勁？唔係<br />\n澳門醫療，基建，大學，政府服務（派錢除外），人材，法制水準都係好低<br />\n<br />\n純粹係因為佢係做啱一樣野：<strong>開放賭業，成為全中國唯一有合法賭場嘅地區，令到全中國啲賭金湧晒入去</strong><br />\n<br />\n假如中國有個垃圾三線城，開放毒品市場，果個垃圾城市都會因為係全球唯一一個合法交易毒品嘅城市，推到GDP全世界第一<br />\n個垃圾三線城GDP高唔代表高質素<br />\n<br />\n為咗唔好益澳門<br />\n我地可以一招欖炒澳門：立即開放賭業，邀請美國賭博公司落戶香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我包保開業後，澳門GDP即跌一半<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:56:54.000Z","msg":"On9 和你塞港澳碼頭係唔係仲實際d呀"},{"pid":"9020ad3417596ebe67a1a63038d504abd18cf6aa","tid":1788392,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:59:18.000Z","msg":"講到港府會配合你咁<br />\non99"},{"pid":"3c17c1bae0d3f642a13090df326f370df3fdf9ea","tid":1788392,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳門GDP咁高，<br />\n係澳門人水準高？唔係<br />\n係澳門政府勁？唔係<br />\n澳門醫療，基建，大學，政府服務（派錢除外），人材，法制水準都係好低<br />\n<br />\n純粹係因為佢係做啱一樣野：<strong>開放賭業，成為全中國唯一有合法賭場嘅地區，令到全中國啲賭金湧晒入去</strong><br />\n<br />\n假如中國有個垃圾三線城，開放毒品市場，果個垃圾城市都會因為係全球唯一一個合法交易毒品嘅城市，推到GDP全世界第一<br />\n個垃圾三線城GDP高唔代表高質素<br />\n<br />\n為咗唔好益澳門<br />\n我地可以一招欖炒澳門：立即開放賭業，邀請美國賭博公司落戶香港 &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;<br />\n我包保開業後，澳門GDP即跌一半<br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你而家至知？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共狗早你廿幾年已經知，更清楚分開兩大洗白白，港豬一個股票賭場，澳狗一個實體賭場嘅好處囉！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e7121d19aa6c8254b1936d4716e49cc58490fcb1","tid":1788392,"uid":257087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:07:51.000Z","msg":"此post已完"},{"pid":"76f14c40a950642f55d5f900a38479c31bebf822","tid":1788392,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:12:32.000Z","msg":"乜9美國公司 只會俾一堆支那公司黎開 <br />\n賺錢既人都係支那"},{"pid":"6d0698781d73c5d19857ae204628b4af670a9f80","tid":1788392,"uid":340074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:13:36.000Z","msg