5d0dc92065518f3d9344","tid":1788392,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港由港足做起<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hong Kong 🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\nOle ole ole<br />\n<br />\n本谷旨在想有興趣睇港足港超或者一路有睇開的球迷入嚟一齊討論傾下波經。以老帶新，由資深球迷帶新手球迷入門，交換資訊，降低香港睇波門檻，等愈來愈多球迷入場撐港足，重建香港球巿。<br />\n<br />\n入group嘅可以講低自己中意邊隊，得閒約埋一齊去睇波。仲等咩快d入嚟<br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6vRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=73909799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a>"},{"pid":"b4a101a97bd606426dd47798f4e569578f7ab7f6","tid":1788392,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698ca0472625a67da330d0a1fd16d401e29dcb52","tid":1788392,"uid":313964,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"都真賭香港波合法化講左幾多萬年"},{"pid":"fe3069c0d6fa3373a1504e61152078b66e881943","tid":1788392,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:26:06.000Z","msg":"香港咁既環境真係唔好攪賭業，黃賭毒真係會招埋好多罪惡同低等人口集合，D人日日研究賭同毒你都死，香港金股樓已經造就左一班無學識無品德既人。"},{"pid":"b27cac8c88eef903d82ec90c14e2aec476cdf81f","tid":1788392,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:27:53.000Z","msg":"羨慕澳門人生活方式慢又水平高工作hea，最重要人工又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人做緊奴隸重要睇唔起人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84261fb7d6cde4f4aef58758e07c589a6b8a473","tid":1788392,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022edb296937a84ff6b1e43c10333e4e7f74d15b","ti