392,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a794df38bfebd4816b2d417ded03967d9d1ce37","tid":1788392,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38d50be45492a89002e6144722413c020b7ea1db","tid":1788392,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e544c0f6a5f8fb7424728c0775469622ce0de9","tid":1788392,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"唔批證俾大陸人入嚟囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"得既話一早唔洗五大訴求啦，你講野牙？！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:56:05.000Z","msg":"做左你都唔知啦。大陸11月已經唔批內地省市簽香港通行證啦，而家嚟到果班係一早簽落。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"以前簽落都大把啦。佢話放就放。<br />\n放就香港陸沉！唔放就樓主講既野完全無用。<br />\n而加就係唔想大陸人落黎，佢地去澳門就得。我地要既唔係GDP，係支共停止浸透，停止逼害香港人，停止響香港攞利益，要去就比佢地去澳門得架喇。<br />\n<br />\n香港不了。"},{"pid":"9d22403aba00c7c7351ff5b44b19b921fcac1d1b","tid":1788392,"uid":213917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a07b44636452639fb6f8d3b0b1aaca80331dd9e9","tid":1788392,"uid":740,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T23:44:46.000Z","msg":"on撚9<br />\n香港金融已經係最大賭場<br />\n澳門之所以比人睇底就係靠賭為收益來源<br />\n香港開賭，先唔講會增加咩大陸人過呢賭<br />\n賭場始終走偏放唔上大檯<br />\n加上一堆放數叠馬搵食，黃賭毒加劇對民生影響<br />\n香港唔係一個大地方，唔可以劃分區域咁做<br />\n提出嗰個有無用過腦？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"因為係張建宗二世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3978dac9d4092b3fa0c7d2229e9514d6e771e199","tid":1788392,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"香港都有賭業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a563b910a817edae5b5f3299cf428ae807ccf85a","tid":1788392,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b17fc63d9f0196f29e90b1ca2ae6327003f52d","tid":1788392,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a794df38bfebd4816b2d417ded03967d9d1ce37","tid":1788392,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38d50be45492a89002e6144722413c020b7ea1db","tid":1788392,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"得既話一早唔洗五大訴求啦，你講野牙？！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:56:05.000Z","msg":"做左你都唔知啦。大陸11月已經唔批內地省市簽香港通行證啦，而家嚟到果班係一早簽落。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"以前簽落都大把啦。佢話放就放。<br />\n放就香港陸沉！唔放就樓主講既野完全無用。<br />\n而加就係唔想大陸人落黎，佢地去澳門就得。我地要既唔係GDP，係支共停止浸透，停止逼害香港人，停止響香港攞利益，要去就比佢地去澳門得架喇。<br />\n<br />\n香港不了。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"香港澳門搞賭根本就會食支那人條水，外國人邊使嚟你呢度賭啊。佢唔放人你個爐起得幾靚都冇用，繼續自己圍爐取暖打飛機啦。"},{"pid":"c1dd3bd471ff1f61af2716f13736ed324409efc7","tid":1788392,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89462bd3744e9730b9777fec43416a15ad7c7ba6","tid":1788392,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳門GDP咁高，<br />\n係澳門人水準高？唔係<br />\n係澳門政府勁？唔係<br />\n澳門醫療，基建，大學，政府服務（派錢除外），人材，法制水準都係好低<br />\n<br />\n純粹係因為佢係做啱一樣野：<strong>開放賭業，成為全中國唯一有合法賭場嘅地區，令到全中國啲賭金湧晒入去</strong><br />\n<br />\n假如中國有個垃圾三線城，開放毒品市場，果個垃圾城市都會因為係全球唯一一個合法交易毒品嘅城市，推到GDP全世界第一<br />\n個垃圾三線城GDP高唔代表高質素<br />\n<br />\n為咗唔好益澳門<br />\n我地可以一招欖炒澳門：立即開放賭業，邀請美國賭博公司落戶香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我包保開業後，澳門GDP即跌一半<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"香港有提岀過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比大陸ban"},{"pid":"2e189cd6b594771879e01b9021a018380aa61839","tid":1788392,"uid":196222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:18:46.000Z","msg":"香港開賭即係將鄰居既自由行分過黎<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"8dfeece322e4205066d89a99d31b45771a646e41","tid":1788392,"uid":201372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"香港好多賭徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9863ec311898a119e7f1d397d3364d60265715f4","tid":1788392,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab9bb42d58eb7ae47f6da78b1b369b017716e228","tid":1788392,"uid":237627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3069c0d6fa3373a1504e61152078b66e881943","tid":1788392,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:26:06.000Z","msg":"香港咁既環境真係唔好攪賭業，黃賭毒真係會招埋好多罪惡同低等人口集合，D人日日研究賭同毒你都死，香港金股樓已經造就左一班無學識無品德既人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"香港人唔比賭咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"邊有得唔比賭架咁大間賭場淨係做大陸人生意?俾人屌撚死啊!"},{"pid":"0988412e76c98b99209c378d354a40ff8efecf29","tid":1788392,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"以前東莞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382b508cde65e8a320db640270231cb9a79056c8","tid":1788392,"uid":101439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"咁講不如香港搞娛樂大麻合法化 但前提係你要KO個政府"},{"pid":"692ba1b6f42e50f081f82dbd9cd3793ce19e4f17","tid":1788392,"uid":26327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:41:13.000Z","msg":"不了， 會有太多平頭大肚腩黑衫versace t  guccu bag 北京腔 食大陸臭煙 嘅中國人"},{"pid":"c0692eb9fc4d727e044c8de604721297d60e7ac0","tid":1788392,"uid":59863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"拆左 迪士尼 起賭場咪得"},{"pid":"5f39848cfce09219ce0983409cf8c06b2c9e7fa0","tid":1788392,"uid":310423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"搵個島仔填大佢起賭場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc6a5924c4916f7b1220524a5178776a771d11e","tid":1788392,"uid":98958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:08:10.000Z","ms